  <brief_title>Physical Activity and Cognitive Behavioural Therapy in Panic Disorder and Agoraphobia</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Influence of Physical Activity (Prior to In-vivo Exposure) on the Effect of Cognitive Behavioural Therapy in Patients With Panic Disorder and Agoraphobia</official_title>
